text: Herøy, Heroy, or Herøya can be ==Places== *Herøy (Møre og Romsdal), a municipality in Møre og Romsdal county, Norway *Herøy (Nordland), a municipality in Nordland county, Norway *Herøya, a suburb of the city of Porsgrunn in Telemark county, Norway ==Other== *Herøy Bridge, a bridge in Herøy Municipality in Møre og Romsdal county, Norway *Herøy Open Air Museum, a museum in Herøy Municipality in Nordland county, Norway
title: Herøy
